pageContext.claim: “Each point -- it doesn't sound like much because, when I first started, we were at 1.2.  Each point is $3.5 trillion and 10 million jobs.”
pageContext.analysis: Quarterly gross domestic product growth was 1.8 percent in the fourth quarter of 2016 and 1.8 percent in the first quarter of 2017.  It was not 1.2 percent.
